{"tid":1465144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"停止互屌，文宣時候到","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:49:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:01:26.000Z","uid":244653,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ec074ad5939383902f2f6f048517f1c17836269a","tid":1465144,"uid":244653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:49:48.000Z","msg":"機場件事做左就做左<br />\n<br />\n大家要學一個中國詞彙叫「定性」<br />\n<br />\n咩叫定性？就係今晚在各大網絡做文宣，先定義個公安係搞事<br />\n<br />\n「中國公安混入和平示威中！」<br />\n「機場內地客內藏木棍，竟是...亅<br />\n「公安鬧事，人民聲討」<br />\n「警方例牌遅到，難道....亅<br />\n「警察開真槍」<br />\n「有人持有我愛HK T-shirt 」<br />\n<br />\n唔需要有真正內容，就算淨標題就ok，總之帶起陰謀論，要學會五毛藍絲手段，先行定性，為行動正當化，各位手足，為今日冇出而自責？出手時候到了，各位盡做啊"},{"pid":"30f462821b6fa2692fb84a59438903230987a67e","tid":1465144,"uid":244653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:50:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"222c8726785dddde1ed22dfc1ea9a969a99cab16","tid":1465144,"uid":244653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:50:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dd9496d425fdc60a0ae62dcd227508cce38df80","tid":1465144,"uid":244653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:51:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a25e8b2f960ddd615b33dbaa204587804df15da5","tid":1465144,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:52:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8.18!!! NOW OR NEVER</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cp1z8r7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcp1z8r7.jpg&h=a68e6149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NgApMdN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNgApMdN.png&h=d2b9e7ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgjmOr7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgjmOr7.jpg&h=35e81e0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SL3VSTN.jpg\